312
00:34:01,320 --> 00:34:14,300
The biggest result that was achieved on these systems, which I personally trust among my acquaintances who deal with this, was 650 W.

313
00:34:15,300 --> 00:34:18,300
No talk about kilowatts goes yet.

314
00:34:19,160 --> 00:34:25,700
Now all is at the stage of lab specimens that show the most interesting results.

315
00:34:26,660 --> 00:34:37,700
